  {
    "key": "556f6a398fcc32ae1535f94c9c7d319cc743f41a809b7548786d26d61fba1117",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_46.png[/img]Thanks to the %companyname%, the shambling monstrosities of the %recently_destroyed% will never again threaten innocent folk. The men, however, will need a few days, and copious amounts of drink, to process the horrors they faced.%SPEECH_ON%How can anything so foul show itself by the light of day?%SPEECH_OFF%Asks %randombrother%, starring blandly into the distance.%SPEECH_ON%It collapsed straight into a heap of rotten bones and dust. Nothing at all holding it together but its curse.%SPEECH_OFF%Even darker fears are sparked for %fearful_brother%.%SPEECH_ON%They told me back in %randomtown% that any good man killed by one of them horrors is doomed to come back from the grave himself and can never sit by the gods.%SPEECH_OFF%Some men argue loudly against this, not because they know better, but because they don't want it to be true. You give the order to bank the fire before someone starts telling any more ghost stories. The men may have trouble sleeping this night, but morale will rise again with the dawn.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.SuccessText = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_46.png[/img]Thanks to the %companyname%, the shambling monstrosities of the %recently_destroyed% will never again threaten innocent folk. The men, however, will need a few days, and copious amounts of drink, to process the horrors they faced.%SPEECH_ON%How can anything so foul show itself by the light of day?%SPEECH_OFF%Asks %randombrother%, starring blandly into the distance.%SPEECH_ON%It collapsed straight into a heap of rotten bones and dust. Nothing at all holding it together but its curse.%SPEECH_OFF%Even darker fears are sparked for %fearful_brother%.%SPEECH_ON%They told me back in %randomtown% that any good man killed by one of them horrors is doomed to come back from the grave himself and can never sit by the gods.%SPEECH_OFF%Some men argue loudly against this, not because they know better, but because they don't want it to be true. You give the order to bank the fire before someone starts telling any more ghost stories. The men may have trouble sleeping this night, but morale will rise again with the dawn.\""
  }
]